/SCD/XXERASH/XX. When senseless hatred reigns on earth and people hide their faces
from one another, then heaven is forced to hide its face. But when love
comes to rule the earth and people reveal their faces to one another, then
the splendor of God will be revealed.    /SC/XXM.B. (ADAPTED)/XX/PR

